description:
FURNISHED UNIT. Spacious, sun-drenched and airy 2-bedroom 2-bathroom condo located on the 2nd floor of a recently renovated 3-unit building on a tree-lined street in South Boston. The apartment features high ceilings and hardwood floors, an in-unit washer/dryer, and a clean storage room in the basement. Upon entry, off the charming kitchen with high-end appliances is a premium living space featuring couches, a 55-inch TV with free use of Netflix and Amazon Prime, Amazon Alexa, smart lights and a wireless charger. Here you will also have access to in-unit laundry with large General Electric Washer and Dryer as well as a vacuum cleaner and a coat closet. Two furnished and organized bedrooms with an ample amount of closet space. Two sanitized bathrooms, of which one is en-suite. Each bedroom is furnished with a queen-size bed, a desk, a dresser, 1 set of bed linen, lamps, and 100 hangers. No pets allowed.

First month's rent, security deposit and broker fee due at lease signing.
